description:
This is a beta test of a Bitcoin blockchain torrent project. Interested participants are invited to try, and comment (chech forum link bellow).

Bitcoin client version 0.7.1, which just entered testing, includes a new feature:

If the file &quot;bootstrap.dat&quot; is found in the bitcoin data directory, it will validate and import all blockchain data found in that file. The following torrent presents a bootstrap.dat file for that feature.

What is bootstrap.dat?

It is a flat, binary file containing bitcoin blockchain data, from the genesis block through height 193,000.  Height 193,000 is the height of the current checkpoint baked into the reference client.
